    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>P.J.'s Act - Amends the Housing and Community Development Act of 1974 to make the acquisition, installation, and maintenance of security cameras, safety lighting, and building locking mechanisms in public housing eligible for community development block grant (CDBG) assistance.</p>]]></text>
